            "title": "買樓送真金！  ONE STANLEY洋房1.38億售出 中港商人入市自住 獲贈236萬足金黃金",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OuOwEBDjcHDMe24tXwpHTA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/28hse_com_210/cc9389b328f39f668d8d264feb154b14\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></div>",
